      <title>景顺调查显示主权财富基金看好新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/sovereign-funds-are-turning-bullish-on-emerging-markets-invesco-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[景顺资产管理公司的年度调查显示，管理着 22 万亿美元资产的主权财富基金和央行预计，新兴市场资产将受益于地缘政治紧张局势的加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/sovereign-funds-are-turning-bullish-on-emerging-markets-invesco-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登退出使特朗普贸易面临不确定性，大选重新开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/biden-exit-leaves-markets-asking-what-s-next-for-trump-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数周以来，投资者一直在押注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，减持长期美国债券，购买比特币等。现在，他们正在考虑乔·拜登退出竞选是否会增加民主党获胜的几率——以及他们必须在多大程度上重新调整他们的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/biden-exit-leaves-markets-asking-what-s-next-for-trump-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 19:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
